1. *Operacija* je uspešno završena. (The operation was successfully completed.)
2. Pacijenti su zahtevali *operaciju*. (The patients requested the operation.)
3. Doktor je spreman za *operaciju*. (The doctor is ready for the operation.)
4. Učestvovali su u *operaciji*. (They participated in the operation.)
5. Očekuje se da će trajati još tri *operacije*. (It is expected that there will be three more operations.)
6. *Operacija* je bila vrlo ozbiljna. (The operation was very serious.)
7. Počeo je sa *operacijom*. (He began the operation.)
8. Odlučili su da izvrše *operaciju*. (They decided to perform the operation.)